data.description: Look no further. 3 bedroom home with open floor plan and vaulted ceilings. Kitchen features breakfast bar and eat in  space. Master bedroom features walk-in closet, dual sinks, Garden tub and  separate shower with glass door. The Sanctuary community offers tennis court and community pool. Great location, near UCF and major roads only minutes from Waterford Lakes shopping center. Needs TLC.
